'S e buidheann de dh'eileanan anns [[a' Chairibìan]] a tha anns na ''' Lesser Antilles'''. Tha iad na laighe air taobh tuath  [[Aimearaga-a-Deas]]  eadar a’ [[Muir Cairibianach|Mhuir Chairibianach]] agus an [[Cuan Siar]]. Anns an iar-thuath tha na  [[Greater Antilles]].

Bha an cuid as motha dhuibh air an cruthachadh mar [[beinn-theine]]. 

Tha dà buidheann anns na Lesser Antilles ris an canar ''Windward Islands'' (sa deas) agus  ''Leeward Islands'' (san tuath).

==Eileanan==   
    
Na h-eileanan as cudthromaiche anns na Lesser Antilles (bho tuath gu deas chun an iar):    
    
'''Leeward Islands''':   
*[[U.S. Virgin Islands]]: [[Saint Thomas, United States Virgin Islands|St. Thomas]], [[Saint John, United States Virgin Islands|St. John]], [[Saint Croix, United States Virgin Islands|St. Croix]]   
*[[British Virgin Islands]]: [[Tortola]], [[Virgin Gorda]], [[Anegada]], [[Jost Van Dyke]]   
*[[Anguilla]] (UK)   
*[[Saint Martin|Saint Martin/Sint Maarten]] (France/Neth. Antilles)   
*[[Saint-Barthélemy]] (Fr.)   
*[[Saba]] (Neth.)   
*[[Sint Eustatius]] (Neth.)   
*[[Naomh Crìstean agus Nibheis|Naomh Crìstean]] neo ''Saint Kitts'' sa Bheurla  
*[[Naomh Crìstean agus Nibheis|Nibheis]] neo ''Nevis'' sa Bheurla   
*[[Antigua agus Barbuda|Barbuda]]   
*[[Antigua agus Barbuda|Antigua]]   
*[[Redonda]]   
*[[Montserrat]] (UK)   
*[[Guadeloupe]] (Fr.)   
*[[La Désirade]] (Fr.)   
*[[Les Saintes]] (Fr.)   
*[[Marie-Galante]] (Fr.)   
*[[Doiminicia]] neo ''Dominica'' sa Bheurla   
    
'''Windward Islands''':   
*[[Martinique]] (Fr.)   
*[[Naomh Lùisia]] neo ''Saint Lucia''  'sa Bheurla   
*[[Barbados]]   
*[[Naomh Bhionsant agus Eileanan Greanadach|Naomh Bhionsant]]  neo ''Saint Vincent''  'sa Bheurla 
*[[Grenadines]]   
*[[Greanada]] neo ''Grenada'' 'sa Bheurla
*[[Trianaid agus Tobago]] neo ''Trinidad and Tobago'' 'sa Bheurla
    
'''Leeward Antilles''' – eileanan air taobh tuath [[A' Bheiniseala|Bheiniseala]], (bhon iar chun an ear):   
*[[Aruba]] (Neth.)   
*[[Curaçao]] (Neth.)   
*[[Bonaire]] (Neth.)   
